Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:06.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Like an angel that has no\Nsense of mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:13.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Rise, young boy, to the heavens\Nlike a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Cold winds, as blue as the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Tear open the door to\Nyour heart, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But unknowing you seem, just\Nstaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:37.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Standing there smiling serenely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Desperate, for something to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,A moment of kindness like\Nthat in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:51.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Of the path your destiny will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But someday you’ll become aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Everything that you’ve got behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:03.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your wings are for seeking out a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Future that only you can search for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:14.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis enters through\Nthe window of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:18.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,If you should betray the chapel\Nof your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis bleeds through\Na portal like your pulsing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,So, boy, stand tall and embrace\Nthe fire of the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:29.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Embracing the universe like\Na blazing star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:39.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The second and third Ashino Lakes, I\Nhope there won’t be any more of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:45.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I received a complaint from Chairman\NKeel yesterday regarding the delay.\NHe came directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:50.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He was very upset.  Towards the end,\Nhe even threatened to dismiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Adam is growing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and work on the dummy plugs for\Nthe Eva Project is proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are the old men of SEELE\Ncomplaining about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The all-important Instrumentality\NProject is behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:06.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All the projects are linked.\NThere are no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Including Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,By the way, what should\Nwe do about that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Leave him alone for now.  The same\Nwith the Marduk Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I agree, let him work for us a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:27.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What started here, 16 years ago?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.52,Background,,0,0,0,Video Text,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\p1}m 0 0 l 720 0 720 540 0 540
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.52,Episode (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\c&H000000&}{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,230)}Episode 15:
Dialogue: 3,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.52,Title (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\c&H000000&}{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,257)}Lie and Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ah, so it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:59.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shannon Bio, a foreign chemical firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:04.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This has been here for nine years, nine\Nyears and not a single change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:10.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Marduk Institute has 108 affiliated\Ncompanies.  106 of them are\Ndummy corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And this is the 107th?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the corporate registration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And you want me to take a look at the\Nboard of directors, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know about it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know all of the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:30.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Marduk is supposedly an advisory\Nbody controlled by the Instrumentality\NCommittee to select Evangelion pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What it really does is not clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:37.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your duty is to investigate NERV.\NGetting involved with the Marduk\NInstitute is inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:43.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, be that as it may, I want to see\Neverything for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Kaji.  I’m out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please leave your name and message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Help me, Kaji!\NDon’t touch me, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’ll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I want to go out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:10.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So I’ve been calling Kaji to ask him to\Ntake me, but he’s been out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s always out lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So you’ll have time tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:18.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Regrettably so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, it’s like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:32.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A friend of my big sister,\NKodama, keeps asking me to\Nintroduce you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,YOU!  Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Necrosis operation complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Graph measurement complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Which dress will you wear tomorrow?\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Synch ratio is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,For the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I wore the pink suit for\NKiyomi’s wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and the dark blue dress for\NKotoko’s shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about the orange one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You haven’t worn that one\Nlately, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, there’s a reason for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Should I get a new one\Non the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s an extra expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve been invited to so many\Nshowers lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that the cost of all the gifts\Nis starting to add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Everyone’s just rushing to get married\Nbefore they’re thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:33.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No one wants to be the\Nlast one still single.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay, you can take off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m tired of these stupid tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:48.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,By the way, Shinji looks even more\Ndowncast than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s because of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:57.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...  I have to see my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What should I talk to him about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why do you ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because I’ve seen you talking\Nhappily with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Say, my father...\Nwhat kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve been watching me because you\Nwanted to ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When we were cleaning today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...you were squeezing the cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The way you squeezed it\Nwas like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:43.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thought it was like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think you’ll make a good\Nmother, Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You’re the one who caused\Nus to break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,I’m home.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}You’re the one who caused\Nus to break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:58.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s up?\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,What’s up?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I was wrong.  I must have been insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,You’d better go to bed.  Aren’t you\Ngoing on a date tomorrow?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I was wrong.  I must have been insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:03.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,You’d better go to bed.  Aren’t you\Ngoing on a date tomorrow?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don’t care how you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Yeah, with a hunk.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don’t care how you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:05.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don’t care how you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I’m different now anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Hey, that’s right, let me use your\Nlavender perfume!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I’m different now anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:09.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Hey, that’s right, let me use your\Nlavender perfume!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Absolutely not.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Jeez, cheapskate!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Jeez, cheapskate!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can’t reverse the hands of a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,It’s not for kids.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can’t reverse the hands of a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Is Shinji in his room?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can’t reverse the hands of a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Is Shinji in his room?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}We can’t go back to that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,He’s been shut up since he got back.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}We can’t go back to that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:17.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,He’s been shut up since he got back.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,It looks like he doesn’t want\Nto see his father.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:19.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,It looks like he doesn’t want\Nto see his father.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I tell you, it’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,If he doesn’t, why doesn’t he just say\Nso.  I don’t understand you Japanese.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I tell you, it’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,If he doesn’t, why doesn’t he just say\Nso.  I don’t understand you Japanese.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It took me three years to forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Well, he doesn’t really hate him...\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It took me three years to forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It took me three years to forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,...that’s the problem.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}It took me three years to forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that’s the problem.\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well done, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you scared?\NOf seeing your father by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unless you step forward,\Nnothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ll begin to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:11.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...after that first step, it’s just as\Nimportant to take another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:15.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anyway, go see him tomorrow with\Nyour chin held high...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...because you’ll be seeing your\Nmother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, you bought a new dress for\Ntomorrow, didn’t you?  Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, you wanna see?\NIt’s an expensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The price doesn’t always\Nreflect the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you pick one to Kaji’s taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t think so.  Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Place three bags in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ladybugs with red, blue\Nand yellow dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, let us proceed with\Nthe reception...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Little Ryo’s late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That idiot has never been on\Ntime in his entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,For your dates, you mean?\NHe’s always on time for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, girls!\NYou look marvelous today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I couldn’t get off work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t believe that,\Nyou never do anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:22.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why didn’t you shave?  That stubble’s\Nawful.  Look, your necktie is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You two act like you’re married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good point, Ri-baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who the hell would marry this dork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been three years since the last time\Nwe came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I ran away then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and haven’t been back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My mother is resting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...I don’t really believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t even remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man survives by forgetting\Nhis memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But there are some things a man\Nshould never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yui taught me about the\Nirreplaceable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I come here to confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You have no pictures of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This grave is merely a decoration, too.\NThere’s no corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So the teacher was right.\NYou threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I keep everything in my heart.\NThat is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s time.  I’m leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:49.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well...  I’m glad...\Nwe could talk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:39.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not bad!  I didn’t know you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve been studying since I was five,\Nbut I’m not very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t really have any talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,“Perseverance is power.”\NI’m impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:51.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I started studying because my\Nteacher told me to, but I could\Nhave quit anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So why didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:55.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because nobody told me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I should have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You came back early.\NI thought you’d have dinner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He was just so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So while he was waiting in line for\Nthe roller coaster, I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really, Kaji is the only cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you gonna leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(150,150)}High heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We haven’t really gotten together to\Ndrink lately, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato’s drinking too much, isn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s acting a little out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:39.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sometimes one drinks to keep oneself\Nunder control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As someone who lived with her, your\Nwords carry a certain weight of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:50.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I did live with her, but that\Nwas before Katsuragi started wearing\Nheels like a real woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s not how we saw it back\Nwhen we were in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:13:00.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That wasn’t really life.\NKid’s play is what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Life isn’t that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I forgot to give you this.\NA souvenir from a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.  You’re very honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Only with the ladies.\NWhen it comes to work, I’m less so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I somehow doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I lost once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not my style to keep fighting a\Nbattle I’m sure to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think you still have a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s my policy to never\Ntalk about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s nothing amusing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why is Katsuragi taking so long?\NFixing her make-up maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What were you doing in Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, that’s from Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t try to fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ll get your fingers burned if you\Nget involved in this too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s the advice of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll take it seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but I’d prefer to be burned by the\Nheat of my passion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Should I buy you some fireworks?\N{\c&H00E3FE&}...but I’d prefer to be burned by the\Nheat of my passion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Should I buy you some fireworks?\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You never change, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:54.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course I change,\Nliving means changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Homeostasis and transistasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,One is a force to maintain the\Nstatus quo, and the other is\Na force for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:05.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anything that contains these two\Nconflicting forces is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Like men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I’ll be leaving now.\NI’ve still got some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji?  It’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:29.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m with Kaji.\NWe’re gonna be out drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes...  okay, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Was it Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, she’ll be late,\Nso don’t wait up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is she gonna stay out until morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t think so, she’s with Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That guarantees it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Drinking so much you throw up like\Na kid!  How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know, but I’m not a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, neither of us are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe you wear high\Nheels now, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Time’s really flown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rough face...  You need to shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can walk now.  Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:19.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji, do you think I’ve changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re even more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry that I insisted on\Nbreaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When I said I had somebody else,\Nyou knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that it was a lie, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s just that I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...you were so much like\Nmy late father, Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...I realized that I wanted a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...like my father, I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Being with you, Kaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...being a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...everything scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hated my father, but fell in love with\Nsomeone just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I chose to break everything\Noff and join NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, it turned out that my father\Nhad worked for NERV, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:20.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I tried to bury my feelings by swearing\Nvengeance against the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That was your decision, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t have to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  That wasn’t a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just escaped from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Escaped from the reality\Ncalled “Father”!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m just like Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m really sorry.  I had to get drunk\Njust to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m just a child myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have no right to tell Shinji anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m a coward!\NI just use men when I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:02.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In the past, Kaji, I may have just...\Njust used you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s enough!  Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t stand myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:33.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji, do you want to kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:33.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}A kiss...  kiss.  You’ve never\Nkissed a girl, have you?\N{\c&H00E3FE&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}A kiss...  kiss.  You’ve never\Nkissed a girl, have you?\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, let’s do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because I’m bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:45.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that a reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you not want to kiss on the\Nanniversary of your mom’s death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:51.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Afraid she may be watching\Nyou from heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:51.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why would I be scared of a kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You brushed your teeth, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stop breathing, it tickles me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:00.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I should never kiss to kill time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All right, here we are.  Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I’ll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you stay with us, Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d be laughed at if I went\Nto work in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’ll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaji, it’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lavender perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Please take care of Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?  You look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s because you kissed me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:57.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, let me call the girls’ roll...\NAyanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayanami’s absent again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi, how are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:46.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sober now, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:51.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this your real job or your other job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:56.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ryoji Kaji of NERV’s Special\NInspection Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:00.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and at the same time Ryoji Kaji of\Nthe Japanese Department of Interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You underestimate NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:06.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this an order from\NCommander Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:10.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, my sole discretion.  If you keep\Ndoing this other job, you’ll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As long as Commander Ikari is using\Nme, too, I can still do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, let me apologize for using\Nyou, Major Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’ll make us even for your\Nhelp yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thanks very much...  but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the Commander and Ritsuko are\Nhiding something from you, too, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva?  No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:47.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the source of\Neverything since the Second Impact.\NThe most important factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Adam?  Why is the First Angel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:58.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know NERV at all.
