Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:13.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s proud, but then he’s swallowed\Nby a Sea of Dirac.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:20.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,With Eva’s energy supply running out,\Nfear, loneliness and cold crash\Nin upon him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:25.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...teaching him a new level of\Nanguish and despair!
